    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-heading">Commercial Finance Solutions</h2>

      <div class="service-card-grid">
        <ServiceCard
          icon="Forklift"
          title="Equipment Finance"
          descriptions={[
            "Equipment finance for Toowoomba businesses covers agricultural machinery, construction equipment, and commercial vehicles. We finance excavators, loaders, and earthmoving equipment for construction contractors, trucks and trailers for transport operators capitalising on Inland Rail opportunities, and utes for trades businesses maintaining reliable fleets. Agricultural equipment finance structures align with seasonal Darling Downs cash flow, supporting tractors, harvesters, grain handling equipment, and irrigation systems. Manufacturing businesses in Wellcamp and Charlton industrial estates access production equipment finance for CNC machinery, food processing equipment, and materials handling systems. Fast approvals and competitive rates ensure equipment finance strengthens your operations."
          ]}
          link="/equipment-finance"
          linkText="Learn More →"
        />
        <ServiceCard
          icon="CashBanknote"
          title="Working Capital Solutions"
          descriptions={[
            "Working capital finance addresses cash flow challenges for Toowoomba businesses facing seasonal income patterns or extended payment terms. Agricultural businesses bridge gaps between harvest revenue and year-round operating expenses without requiring asset security. Construction companies secure funding to purchase materials, pay subcontractors, and cover wages while awaiting progress payments on major commercial developments. Growth initiatives require investment before returns arrive—inventory finance supports stock purchases for peak seasons, while working capital funds market expansion or new service launches. Bridge financing provides short-term funding for businesses awaiting property settlements, insurance payouts, or contract payments. Flexible working capital solutions respond to regional business cycles."
          ]}
          link="/working-capital-finance"
          linkText="Learn More →"
        />
        <ServiceCard
          icon="Building"
          title="Commercial Property Loans"
          descriptions={[
            "Commercial property finance supports workshop purchases, industrial warehouse investments, and depot expansions for Toowoomba businesses. Trade businesses operating from residential properties face council restrictions and limited growth capacity. Purchasing commercial property in Harristown, Charlton, or Wellcamp industrial estates provides legitimate business premises with equipment storage, workforce expansion, and enhanced professional credibility. Industrial property in Wellcamp's growing precinct represents strategic investment for logistics and manufacturing operations. Commercial property loans feature competitive interest rates and flexible deposit requirements, enabling purchases without exhausting business cash reserves. Investment properties in Toowoomba's CBD offer additional income streams and capital growth potential for commercial business owners."
          ]}
          link="/commercial-property-finance"
          linkText="Learn More →"
        />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

