      <div class="service-area-text">
        <p>We provide Queensland-wide business finance services, but our Toowoomba focus ensures we understand regional business challenges. Seasonal agricultural patterns, construction project timing, and Inland Rail infrastructure opportunities all influence when Toowoomba businesses need finance solutions. Whether you operate from the Toowoomba CBD, Wellcamp industrial precinct, or rural Darling Downs properties, we deliver business loans tailored to local market conditions.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="contact-info">
        <p><strong>Phone:</strong> 1300 280 895</p>
        <p><strong>Email:</strong> enquiries@edgeviewfinance.com.au</p>
        <p><strong>Coverage:</strong> All Toowoomba suburbs and Darling Downs region across Southern Queensland</p>
      </div>

      <div class="cta-container">
        <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary btn-lg">
